{"title":"南国之鹰——五好战士速写","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国之鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——五好战士速写"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张仲明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百个战士里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眼能看出你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并非你胸前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂满了荣誉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令人注目的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是淳朴的笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引人深思的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是褪色的军衣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走过多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的山川？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你战胜多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的风雨？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严峻的雪山啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还扬首惊叹："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你忍饥挨冻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把叛匪追击！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你身负重伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还抢背双枪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你痛得昏迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还高喊杀敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动的南海呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正日夜欢呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有枪声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里就有你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心守边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不脱军装；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年如一日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你紧扣扳机！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一株"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满身红花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向阳开！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮志凌云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人惧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你高大的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在队列里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友们纷纷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你看齐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄祖示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的事迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不出奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全场的英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却听得入迷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的武器呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是防毒衣具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上它行军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你昏倒又爬起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了锻炼呼吸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你戴着面具睡觉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了战场过硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你戴着面具射击！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你戴着面具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精读主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你戴着面具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写学习笔记！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你终于在盛夏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的山地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不到一小时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔跑一万米！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！黄祖示呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我认出了你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是从你的面貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是从你顽强的脾气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在韶山冲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上台斗过地主；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你代表社员们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进城领过奖旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在生产队里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和富农辩论；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在青年水库"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带头挖泥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在主席旧居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣誓入党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在矽矿山上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿起军衣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我们时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的标志！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是党的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋的弟弟！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余真　插图"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}